column3: Forgive me, <If(PlayerParameter(4))>miss<Else/>sir</If>, but I deal only in sky pirate spoils, and you haven't got any.
Terribly sorry, but unless you have sky pirate spoils, I'm afraid we cannot do business.
Got spoils? 'Fraid I can't help you then, <If(PlayerParameter(4))>miss<Else/>mate</If>.
We only accept a particular currency here, and that's sky pirate spoils. I gather you have none? Right, then.
If you come into possession of sky pirate spoils, I should be glad to trade with you.
